{"tid":1107627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿搶生意　南亞漢糾眾伏擊同鄉","createTime":"2019-04-15T11:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T12:26:02.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac575630a7bc7c95e2261ef32e5c74e463f78d8","tid":1107627,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190414/photo/bkn-20190414214418971-0414_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190414235325\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190414%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190414214418971-0414_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190414235325&h=711b8e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西營盤干諾道西118號，今晚(14日)8時許，一名南亞漢擬進入上址馬會投注站期間，突遭約5名同鄉手持雨傘及玻璃樽施襲，事主手無寸鐵且猝不及防，慘遭「爆樽」血流如注，兇徒逞兇後四散逃去，途人見狀協助報警。 <br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕至，召救護車把傷者送往瑪麗醫院治理，經初步調查後，案件暫列作襲擊致造成實際身體傷害。據悉，事主為一間網上外賣速遞平台員工，其中一名兇徒為前員工，雙方共事期間，曾因接單問題爭執，有人不滿事主「搶晒啲訂單做」，不排除有人懷恨在心，離職後糾眾持武器伏擊事主。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ImpassionedGlitteringAdamsstaghornedbeetle-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FImpassionedGlitteringAdamsstaghornedbeetle-size_restricted.gif&h=142bfb7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15bbb2099a9fdce10553f4dfc7af87bb2a343053","tid":1107627,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"let them fight<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d997db2c21c602364ee1fc4e05e5f788dbfe36","tid":1107627,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"張超雄"},{"pid":"e9c110c3e1911c34e2b6f281a5f7dbaf0c2037c7","tid":1107627,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"做foodpanda都做到要伏人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}